      "author": "IkariKr",
      "description": "## EPUB Reader Plus 1.0.0\n\nFirst independent release of EPUB Reader Plus.\n\n### Highlights\n\n- Single-page paginated reading with mouse-wheel navigation.\n- Theme-aware backgrounds and publisher EPUB typography.\n- Flat table of contents, responsive reflow, and visible-text font-size anchoring.\n\n### Migration\n\nDisable the original **ePub Reader** plugin before enabling EPUB Reader Plus. Per-book reading positions are preserved by book name; settings begin with the new defaults.\n\n### Attribution\n\nIndependently maintained derivative of [caronchen/obsidian-epub-plugin](https://github.com/caronchen/obsidian-epub-plugin), distributed under the MIT License with the original copyright notice retained.",
